STEPS TO COMPILE AND RUN  CLIENT-SERVER FILES

Open a terminal for server 
1. Open a terminal 
2. Type make 
executable files will be generated 
3. Type chat_server.x serverconfig.txt to execute the server 

******************************************************************

Open 7 terminals for clients, We are allowing maximum of 7  terminals, with maximum of 7 users 
1. Open a terminal 
2. Type make - executable files get generated
3. Type chat_client.x clientconfig.txt to execute the client
